results.name: Triangle read by columns: Distinct classifications of N elements containing exactly R binary partitions.
comment: The bottom of each column is marked by a single 0 in this sequence. Value is 0 for all (N,R) for which N is greater than 2^R.
See note on efficient computation in A171871.
xref: First term in each column is A000055(R+1).
Column 4 shares terms with A034189, column 5 with A034190.
results.author: _Robert Munafo_, Jan 21 2010
